{"tid":428534,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV迷壞消息　三上悠亞從良明年進軍K-pop","createTime":"2017-10-08T06:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T11:55:17.000Z","uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"aeede51520e94ca9c2a4b998bb7358a2243b552a","tid":428534,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"在亞洲深受宅男喜愛的日本AV女神三上悠亞，計劃效法AV前輩蒼井空從良，明年以K-pop的偶像身份進軍韓國藝能界。<br />\n<br />\n三上過往拍了不少AV，在韓國擁有不少男粉絲，月初她在韓國首爾舉行粉絲聚會，反應甚佳，令三上信心大增決定脫離日本AV界，改而從良進軍K-pop以偶像身份出道。三上在聚會上表示自己熱愛K-pop，到過韓國起碼有10次，三上曾在YouTube公開模仿韓國女團TWICE的《SIGNAL》、A Pink的《Cause you're my star》以及GFRIEND的《LOVE WHISPER》等歌曲的舞步，早已虜獲韓迷的歡心。三上在活動更透露明年初會進軍韓國K-pop，也有可能加入韓國女團，從此跟AV界講拜拜。不過，呢個消息對一班AV迷來說，卻是個極壞消息。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171008/mobile/bkn-20171008114606665-1008_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171008%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171008114606665-1008_00862_001.html&d=QmfjLShgqAiVY21BAA36m9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=92604ba4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171008/mobile/bkn-20171008114606665-1008_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db0003e12228aa0b56a7f036a1917af5b3336291","tid":428534,"uid":34444,"like":416,"dislike":14,"score":402,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺三上拍嘅av好睇 假到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d0b3d7fe95d2f1517be21ab02827c86a040357","tid":428534,"uid":150483,"like":251,"dislike":1,"score":250,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"咁同返akb有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18eec5c2b8bfe397bd24723b0eb6de66cef5515","tid":428534,"uid":22694,"like":20,"dislike":20,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺三上拍嘅av好睇 假到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店果幾套j死人喎<img src=\"/assets/fa